description: This file defines Pydantic data schemas for user, team, and authentication data used in an API, including classes for user data, email/password authentication, team data, and team identifiers.

classes.name: UserSchema
classes.description: Schema for user data returned by the API.

classes.name: TeamSchema
classes.description: Schema for team data returned by the API.

classes.name: TeamIdentifier
classes.description: Schema for identifying a team by ID or URL.
